{"tid":470191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲c奶真係好撚自私","createTime":"2017-11-16T05:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T06:28:32.000Z","uid":144820,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"368ed7371a44de05b22c189e4a540f31d2b73927","tid":470191,"uid":144820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"今日番學前出左食飯 由於我住上水 大家都知上水有幾熱鬧 想搵個地方食飯都係咁難 唯一一個冇乜人既食肆就係火車站附近既吉野家 咁我唯有去果到食 雖然平時都係 食到大半 啲中學生放飯 由於果時候已經冇一張檯係吉 咁我諗住我自己一個坐四人位（我去果時都幾多位下）咁我就食快少少啦 比個位比啲中學生啦 突然間我格離個c奶坐左我同檯 我望一望佢個女（我格離張檯）再望一望佢 屌 兩條友做乜分檯坐 佢個女係同一個男人（唔識既）坐埋一齊 點知個女另一邊張檯條友走左 佢個女指左張檯 意思叫佢啊媽坐過去 屌你明知多人黎食飯 你就坐定定係到啦 仲想兩條友霸張吉檯 你食個吉野家要幾耐啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c9f1cf63975d134aa63e67de11d631a3de3c1c","tid":470191,"uid":144820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/133554_055e9834f01383e3e002c13bf2891e55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F133554_055e9834f01383e3e002c13bf2891e55.jpg&h=7ea1afc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afb0b8527d93dd6109637484498909d49fd41fde","tid":470191,"uid":155080,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"對唔住我誤會了&quot;C奶&quot;嘅意思，我出返去先.."},{"pid":"b1d8c711048e600e7998c2812bdeca9b94ae65ab","tid":470191,"uid":144820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對唔住我誤會了&quot;C奶&quot;嘅意思，我出返去先..</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadcbe7e61fedd35ccec8b637f0f1e098cc6f9d2","tid":470191,"uid":125469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對唔住我誤會了&quot;C奶&quot;嘅意思，我出返去先..</blockquote><br />\n大家咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.g